</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06026001">
<title>
Precautions
</title>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Follow instructions below when repairing body part filled with foamed material because such foamed material may start fire when heated.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not heat or cut panels with gas torch or the like.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Use a fire-free tools such as air-saw when cutting panels.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Remove foamed material close to welding part before welding.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
</servinfosub>
